### Order Service API Tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8088/actuator/health

### Create Order from Cart
POST http://localhost:8088/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "shippingAddressId": 1,
  "shippingValue": 15.99,
  "couponCode": "SAVE20",
  "notes": "Please deliver in the morning"
}

### Get User's Order History
GET http://localhost:8088/orders?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get Order by ID
GET http://localhost:8088/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Cancel Order (Admin Only)
PATCH http://localhost:8088/admin/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Admin Endpoints (Require ADMIN Role)

### Get All Orders (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8088/admin/orders?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get Order by ID (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8088/admin/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Update Order Status (Admin)
PATCH http://localhost:8088/admin/orders/1/status?status=CONFIRMED
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Swagger UI
GET http://localhost:8088/swagger-ui
